{"tid":1780184,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"【黃色經濟圈 – Step 3】[民主公司] 進行 [業務複製]","createTime":"2019-12-12T07:26:31.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-13T05:22:53.000Z","uid":135332,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"9696dd5d540bb1d9724b907640ac212f5276b1de","tid":1780184,"uid":135332,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-12T07:26:31.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>目標：</strong></span>令<span style=\"color: red;\">各行各業</span>都有黃色民主公司，香港人可<span style=\"color: red;\">按理念安心消費</span><br />\n<br />\n當然第一樣要商榷的是，何謂民主公司，即是<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">如何才認證一間公司是真民主公司</span></span>？ 我認為，<span style=\"color: green;\">必須具備以下的條件</span>：<br />\n1) 每月捐出利潤 <span style=\"color: red;\">20-50%</span> ，助社運目的<br />\n2) 給予<span style=\"color: red;\">抗爭者工作機會</span><br />\n3) 革新公司架構，要成為民主企業，須讓員工[或消費者]一人一票投票選出管理班底/重要策略 (可待公司營運穩定後，或參考外國例子)<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">被大眾認證的民主公司，有咩著數？</span><br />\n現時香港消費群會因公司理念而消費，受大眾認可的民主公司將<span style=\"color: red;\">成為消費者率先考慮對象</span>。<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\"><br />\n業務複製對象？</span><br />\n產品辨認度不高 (homogeneous product) / <span style=\"color: red;\">已赤化的</span>行業。<br />\n例如：順豐 SF / 即用即棄碗筷 &hellip; <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">模擬例子：</span><br />\n1) 照抄現時順豐SF模式，打造新一間速運公司。公司答應捐出利潤等等，獲取了民主認證，香港人以後寄件會率先考慮。當然價格可能略貴/服務仍未完善，但相信香港人可以包容一下，就好似包容[光時]咁。<br />\n2) 香港現時大部分黃店用的碗筷/塑膠/塑袋都是Made in China，有意開民主公司的製造商可於越南/柬埔寨設廠，獲取民主認證後，所有黃店會改用產品。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: purple;\">=================</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: purple;\">概念是增強經濟圏。細節可以商量。香港眼睛是雪亮的。</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">同意，請推上熱門，致創業人。</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e7c439d09235203aaa77c55f5305e1e7fc0b9847","tid":1780184,"uid":135332,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-12T07:27:13.000Z","msg":"好主意。推。"},{"pid":"84f7ec67bd019595b86b147be259d0696a14e1ea","tid":1780184,"uid":135332,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-12T07:27:24.000Z","msg":"真不錯"},{"pid":"16d721f8f7958236cefa1eb29593a4a21fdefad0","tid":1780184,"uid":135332,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-12T07:27:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a2ce2fbf8470f241d09366099a8ac7e9e634d5da","tid":1780184,"uid":135332,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-12T07:27:49.000Z","msg":"好波。"},{"pid":"b0d044998825f7911e1078c068253589cfb3e961","tid":1780184,"uid":135332,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-12T07:28:08.000Z","msg":"加油，香港人。"},{"pid":"ce69e40d77653b47430488e0f63792ffc1d2e4ff","tid":1780184,"uid":135332,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-12T07:29:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"08eb73044c755f851b4e8409345525bd0f8d0b57","tid":1780184,"uid":135332,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-12T07:31:18.000Z","msg":"民主公司 推"},{"pid":"7592d76478508f2ff6cfadbcb789739927c8ad2d","tid":1780184,"uid":336769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-12T07:33:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n推，邊個想創業想發逹，快推。"},{"pid":"647ad1815f005ca6c78cc645c6cadfb5c03374ae","tid":1780184,"uid":135332,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-12T07:37:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f32fa7da9a886c4cc5f75ce965df9576fc455d78","tid":1780184,"uid":336769,"like":0